    'description' => 'Generate a dated markdown digest from multiple live data sources. Fetches data from HackerNews (top stories), Open-Meteo (weather), GitHub (trending repos via search), and optional RSS feeds. Composes all results into a well-formatted markdown report and writes it to the workspace. Designed to be called unattended (e.g. from cron). Never throws — all errors returned as structured data.',
    'parameters' => 
